{"tid":488101,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"求分享旺角午餐好去處","createTime":"2017-12-03T11:29:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-03T14:15:17.000Z","uid":78509,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"47ffc183f4017f419e9a25218d65959b8b6143a6","tid":488101,"uid":78509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T11:29:56.000Z","msg":"平時自己就去開熟食中心<br />\n有無巴絲有好介紹<br />\n同埋想問 旺角有無啲廿幾蚊麵 類似雲吞麵個啲 因為小弟想草下錢 所以係食個方面減低個支出<br />\n我知可以帶飯 但係公司環境唔容許我咁做 所以唯有食平少少 Thanks<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d5af1f78c5acfa82819e27c63872a94607004c9","tid":488101,"uid":144784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T11:34:24.000Z","msg":"記得有間食牛丸河廿蚊一碗 冇記錯應該係新之城對面<br />\n另外再唔夠飽咪龍津囉<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唉仆你個街唔記得執撚咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"792f6270be3400750692873916454451f5c2f6d0","tid":488101,"uid":73803,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T12:21:57.000Z","msg":"新寶 果條街有一間食潮州麵，都係二十幾"},{"pid":"ea323c1aadc040724a4faa5df7957e756e11b7a6","tid":488101,"uid":78509,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T14:15:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>新寶 果條街有一間食潮州麵，都係二十幾</blockquote><br />\n聽日去試試 唔該巴打"}]}